property.value: Traveler, you've returned... or have you just arrived? In this place we're binded eternally. Your quest is meaningless. We are all prisoners here.

property.name: text
property.value: A king's splendor, built on borrowed time. The Dreamer's eye sees all, and eternity's price is paid in echoes of stolen grace.

properties.property:
Well, look what we have here. A fresh face. Stumbled in from the outside, have we? You're either very brave, or very foolish.
Luckily for you, I can spare you some wisdom, save you some pain. Keep you from making the same mistakes we all did. I know all about the Crawlers in the dungeon, and why you should fear the green gardens... But that knowledge has a price. Show me what you have to offer for it.
Hmph. Empty-handed. How... disappointing. A waste of my breath. Don't think this conversation was free. Time is valueable... and you've wasted mine. You owe me now... and I always make sure the debt is paid.

You... you're not one of them, are you? A new face... an outsider. Are you here for glory? Same as we all, I wished for a hero's death, a legend for the ages... but the ages are long here, and there's no story left to be told. This castle... it's not what they say. It's a gilded cage, lost to time. I'm just so tired.
You have to turn back. Don't fall for the gilded promises of this place. There is no end here. Only... this.
